{"tid":1005722,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求教]東京近郊賞雪","createTime":"2019-02-02T12:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T15:20:24.000Z","uid":74901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"72c0c26236c1c8e50d3e9154c2ffebed4d0aebde","tid":1005722,"uid":74901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"二月中會去東京<br />\n諗住其中一日即日來回去睇雪<br />\n因為純粹想睇下景玩下雪 唔打算滑雪<br />\n所以唔諗住去滑雪場<br />\n搵過下資料 暫時睇中下面三個地點<br />\n日光 河口湖 長野地獄谷<br />\n仲有無其他推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日光同河口湖會唔會得好少雪？<br />\n呢兩個地方暫時積雪都唔多<br />\n因為未睇過雪 想確保睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e70e174218dd6dbf00cdf3427e780bad2fb199","tid":1005722,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0d1fbec901144b59a64053a7050cdf912805dae","tid":1005722,"uid":196552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"長野地獄谷<br />\n東京近郊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔笑你住<br />\n東京呢個一月淨係落過一日雨<br />\n好近既東京既應該真係完全冇雪<br />\n睇氣象廳<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/amedas/206.html?elementCode=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jma.go.jp%2Fjp%2Famedas%2F206.html%3FelementCode%3D4&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2ajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=7a7c7c38\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/amedas/206.html?elementCode=4</a><br />\n最近都要要群馬北部先有積雪<br />\n就咁睇日光中禪寺湖都有少少積雪量<br />\n群馬草津果頭就多少少咁"},{"pid":"942a29112ac86100f13ccc4d3286744e1ffe9787","tid":1005722,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db096e2db5a286caf64b401f704aa97ffb674dbb","tid":1005722,"uid":196552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"942a29112ac861